append d·ªØ li·ªáu c·ªßa ACCUM_W1.csv v√† append d·ªØ li·ªáu 2 file ACCUM_W1.csv, ACCUM_W2.csv, n·∫øu hi·ªán t·∫°i l√† tu·∫ßn th·ª© 4 th√¨ ta s·∫Ω x√≥a c√°c d·ªØ li·ªáu trong file "C:\Users\458714\Downloads\Weekly Forecast _ Cut-off Data.xlsx" c√≥ gi√° tr·ªã ·ªü c·ªôt PERIOD = value ·ªü c·ªôt YearMonth c·ªßa file append d·ªØ li·ªáu c·ªßa ACCUM_W1.csv v√† append d·ªØ li·ªáu 3 file ACCUM_W1.csv, ACCUM_W2.csv, ACCUM_W3.csv, sau khi d·ªØ li·ªáu ƒë∆∞·ª£c append v√†o th√¨ sort theo Period-week, sau khi append code kh√¥ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c thay ƒë·ªïi format v√† c√°c d·ªØ li·ªáu kh√°c ngo√†i c√°c c·ªôt ƒë√£ cho th√¨ kh√¥ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c thay ƒë·ªïi
